Angel,com,provides,interactive,voice,response,systems,for,what,it,calls,on,demand,customer,experience,solutions,The,company,s,platform,specifically,addresses,the,retail,pharmaceutical,financial,high,tech,healthcare,telecommunications,and,travel,industries,However,the,Angel,OutBound,API,provides,tools,so,that,any,developer,can,programatically,instruct,Angel,com,to,place,phone,calls,on,your,behalf,The,API,supports,both,SOAP,and,XML,RPC,protocols,and,returns,results,in,XML